{"tid":1913330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用返區議會結果去配票","createTime":"2020-03-06T16:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T05:54:15.000Z","uid":27250,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c28784f9f6c8d6383b8d12fb3f187b362e4402","tid":1913330,"uid":27250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"基本上都可以做到少數派嘅配票效果"},{"pid":"19f12f584f61c461d96fb201e9cf64a426d9038e","tid":1913330,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"比區選減5%，用生日月份配，咁就應該穩<br />\n但前題係要初選，如果唔團結打選戰，做咩都冇用"},{"pid":"221a5624f01c03c69df338a42f426c4371c38832","tid":1913330,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4d1154442d881824cb23d53e80485ab55e583a3","tid":1913330,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"19f12f584f61c461d96fb201e9cf64a426d9038e","tid":1913330,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"比區選減5%，用生日月份配，咁就應該穩<br />\n但前題係要初選，如果唔團結打選戰，做咩都冇用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"直頭用地區黎配仲準"},{"pid":"2dc0d2af4efe1a89d03ad91cc91dac6b25071b62","tid":1913330,"uid":13467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a4d1154442d881824cb23d53e80485ab55e583a3","tid":1913330,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"19f12f584f61c461d96fb201e9cf64a426d9038e","tid":1913330,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"比區選減5%，用生日月份配，咁就應該穩<br />\n但前題係要初選，如果唔團結打選戰，做咩都冇用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"直頭用地區黎配仲準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"地區配一定準啲<br />\n原本就掌握到各票站投票率<br />\n易過跟生日好多"},{"pid":"985b2c7ffac92c35251b12d949ffa905785f13e2","tid":1913330,"uid":85252,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"跟生日個難處係個黃絲都好多人唔識計數<br />\n跟地區嘅優點係<br />\n宣傳都可以分區<br />\n各候選人河水不犯井水咁去做<br />\n包圍式宣傳，落街見親都係同一個人<br />\n咁就侯選人同選民都易做人"},{"pid":"9514dbf299f029dfaf5b8af0dda52e6212edd8fc","tid":1913330,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"生日月份配票法"},{"pid":"d43851900863814bb694a99d7173c6788c1b7703","tid":1913330,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"地區配票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a052828f74c08011a49bc607f0ece3e0698d2f86","tid":1913330,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19f12f584f61c461d96fb201e9cf64a426d9038e","tid":1913330,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"比區選減5%，用生日月份配，咁就應該穩<br />\n但前題係要初選，如果唔團結打選戰，做咩都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiZ0oCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiZ0oCq.jpg&h=db1d399c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXW2BXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXW2BXq.jpg&h=36ca4b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上屆鳩投結果，益左兩個契仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亂投果班0n99,無大局觀念，以為投心儀既就=贏左"},{"pid":"d4cc35cc0cc09df7091654e919e22661b4b62681","tid":1913330,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"得"},{"pid":"a56056d1feebd2d941ade6fa1aba225835aa1994","tid":1913330,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d1154442d881824cb23d53e80485ab55e583a3","tid":1913330,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"19f12f584f61c461d96fb201e9cf64a426d9038e","tid":1913330,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"比區選減5%，用生日月份配，咁就應該穩<br />\n但前題係要初選，如果唔團結打選戰，做咩都冇用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"直頭用地區黎配仲準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"啱 參考區選就當然係要地區配票"},{"pid":"855ead7cc7982d109a679b10ea6367976b6aedae","tid":1913330,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a0fa933116963224a8ce35551a03e9613275653","tid":1913330,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"不過最大問題係點樣宣傳到每一個人逗知 都識投"},{"pid":"4bbe5833f3f777559beb3893cff005f09dc5d08b","tid":1913330,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0fa933116963224a8ce35551a03e9613275653","tid":1913330,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"不過最大問題係點樣宣傳到每一個人逗知 都識投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"都 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527e25bd3c8a3ac94190eaee2ace921c88d4d116","tid":1913330,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f16113d8a4bf44e406496df6682e06a0b4dd140","tid":1913330,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:32:43.000Z","msg":"以九東為例<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBSxeMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBSxeMJ.jpg&h=29a4922f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMdkoE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMdkoE3.jpg&h=a1056bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九東65個區議會選區<br />\n三張名單每人分配21-22個小區<br />\n組成3個總共86000票嘅大區<br />\n<br />\n好處係：<br />\n可以同每區區議員/社區主任配對拉票<br />\n集中宣傳其中一個大區 節省選舉開支<br />\n唔使選民自己組3人小組咁麻煩"},{"pid":"2ef7aa4fe50a5f5e5210d056da1b9bb0ad583168","tid":1913330,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0fa933116963224a8ce35551a03e9613275653","tid":1913330,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"不過最大問題係點樣宣傳到每一個人逗知 都識投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"靠區議員幫手"},{"pid":"393f5cf519a8fadd508ecfc67e0bcdd4f2c3b008","tid":1913330,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:36:07.000Z","msg":"用區議會按地區來配最好，因為大致已知道每個細區自己友既票係幾多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以九龍東為例， 如果泛民出三隊（1#  2# 3#）<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙、樂富、橫頭磡、竹園邨、新蒲崗、東頭邨<br />\n（投1#）<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山、鑽石山、牛池灣、九龍灣、牛頭角<br />\n（投2#）<br />\n<br />\n觀塘、四順、秀茂坪、藍田、油塘 <br />\n（投3#）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過真係需要有個大台去整合，同指揮"},{"pid":"a6511921931da0e2040492ca6d36077c8a4fd68b","tid":1913330,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f16113d8a4bf44e406496df6682e06a0b4dd140","tid":1913330,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:32:43.000Z","msg":"以九東為例<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBSxeMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBSxeMJ.jpg&h=29a4922f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMdkoE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMdkoE3.jpg&h=a1056bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九東65個區議會選區<br />\n三張名單每人分配21-22個小區<br />\n組成3個總共86000票嘅大區<br />\n<br />\n好處係：<br />\n可以同每區區議員/社區主任配對拉票<br />\n集中宣傳其中一個大區 節省選舉開支<br />\n唔使選民自己組3人小組咁麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"假設九龍東係民主黨、公民黨、黃之鋒/梁凱晴三張名單喺初選出線<br />\n民主黨有15個區議員 搵多6個區議員/地區主任幫手 總共21區<br />\n公民黨有六個 搵多15個區議員/地區主任幫手 總共21區<br />\n梁凱晴本身有自己相熟素人區議員 再搵埋其餘區議員/地區主任 總共21/22個幫手就得<br />\n獲分配嘅區議會選區全投嗰張名單就得"},{"pid":"a3477b6573e57575424b9b5ea1e1306e408a64ee","tid":1913330,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"其實而家要搞初選or配票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00672d4d16651c0f26c75f56b889b33321510a9","tid":1913330,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"嗰區要幾多席咪幾多人一組，一人揀一個投<br />\n<br />\n唔少人有佢自己嘅可接受範圍，唔係你硬塞邊個俾佢佢都老奉會投"},{"pid":"78a771f36cf02d7d9e8b63bb72473230e5462b76","tid":1913330,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"九東最多都係只能夠拎到三席，三條隊無得輸"},{"pid":"100fe8c12decfdfcb24b46a78ebdbc0313f7a907","tid":1913330,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b00672d4d16651c0f26c75f56b889b33321510a9","tid":1913330,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"嗰區要幾多席咪幾多人一組，一人揀一個投<br />\n<br />\n唔少人有佢自己嘅可接受範圍，唔係你硬塞邊個俾佢佢都老奉會投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"呢D咪鳩投囉，純粹主觀意願，無齊上齊落既思想<br />\n<br />\n以為投心儀就等如可以自我感覺良好，好心做壞事益左對家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7K0oMP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7K0oMP.jpg&h=da5d4016&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c3b24e5cf87ec2492692faa327fe668f6c8a3e3","tid":1913330,"uid":306337,"like":0,"disli